                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-9-off57 t18270712-9-cd58"></join>, (he and others being therein) and stealing 1 bed quilt, value 5s., and 1 shawl, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270712-9-victim134" type="victimName">
                        Hannah 
                        Bick
                     <interp inst="t18270712-9-victim134" type="surname" value="Bick"></interp>
